{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_01_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 トップを取るのは私達",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Turning back the clock…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリの開催が迫る最中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――As the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix approaches",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 5.666666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ貴方は\n三枝さんの所の……お名前はなんだったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you’re from Saegusa-san’s…\nMy apologies‚ I forgot your name.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "名刺、いただける？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "May I have your business card?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "先日はうちの子達がお世話になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for taking care of our girls the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 400.00000000000034,
          "startTime": 15.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央は渡された名刺を見もせず、机に置いた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――but she just lays it on the table without taking a glance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "あの子達の様子はどう？\n私達とレッスンした後、落ち込んでるんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are they doing?\nDid they feel discouraged after our joint lesson?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あの時はそれなりに……でもあれくらいで\n落ち込んでいたら、この業界でやっていけません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A little at the time… but it’s something\nthey need to learn to deal with to survive in this business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "それより、貴方はどうしてここに？\nまたあの子達のレッスンなのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ why are you here?\nAre you here for their lessons again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は――あ、失礼しました\n私はダンススタジオの先生と打ち合わせです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m here…Opps‚ sorry‚ I have meetings\nwith the dance coaches at the studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいわよ\n俺でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to apologize.\nEven if it was me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ貴方とそう会うこともないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't be seeing you that often anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（ん？　やけに俺のコンビニ袋を見てるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Hm? She’s staring at the stuff I bought from the convenience store.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、これ人気の季節限定シュークリームです\nたまたま一個だけあったんで買っちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ it’s their special seasonal cream puff.\nThe store had one left‚ so I decided to pick it up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "そう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（あれ、視線がさっきより泳いでるような？）\n（もしかして……お腹が減って気が立ってるんだろうか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Her gaze is wandering…)\n(Wait… Is she hungry?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あの、良かったらどうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can have it if you want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "い、いらないわ、持って帰って\n大体貴方が食べるつもりだったんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ I’m fine. You bought\nto eat yourself‚ didn’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、人気なのでなんとなく買っただけなんです\n先日のお礼ということで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I only really bought it because it was popular.\nConsider it a token of appreciation for the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……お礼\nそう、お礼なのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Appreciation…\nI see‚ a token of appreciation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなら\nいただくわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚\nthank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "断るのも悪いし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be rude to refuse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、貴方は、どうしてこの業界に入ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ why did you join this industry?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "……長瀬麻奈に誘われた？\n一緒に事務所に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You were invited by Mana Nagase\nto join her agency?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "……そう、貴方がいなければ長瀬麻奈は\nそもそもアイドルにならなかったということね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… without you‚ Mana Nagase\nwould never have become an idol in the first place…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん、男の人にとって\n仕事ってとても大切よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ a man’s career\nis the most important decision they’ll make in their life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "そんな大切なことを\nクラスメイトの女の子の一言で決めちゃうなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To make such an important decision\nbased on the single request of a female classmate…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "貴方、どうかしてるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re out of your mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5133.333333333326,
