      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――莉央は机の上の名刺を取り、ひらりと床に落とした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio takes the card from the table and drops it on the ground.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "あの子はもういないんだから\n貴方も辞めればいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s not around anymore.\nWhy are you still here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "この業界は単なるいい人じゃ務まらないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t make it in this industry by just being nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "名刺を捨てたのは、そういう意味ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that why you threw away my business card?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐいなくなる人の名刺を\n持っている意味はないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the point of holding on to the business card\nof someone who won’t be around much longer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "少なくとも今担当してる子達が一人前になるまでは\n辞めません、今後ともよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to disappoint you‚ but I don’t intend to quit\nuntil the girls under my charge can stand on their own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
