      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_01-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "……根性だけはあるようね\nでもトップを取るのは私達よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ll give you credit for your determination.\nBut the top spot belongs to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": [
